public class ProgressAggregate
extends ProgressDelegate

Implementation of ProgressReporting that reports progress based on the totals of sum number of child ProgressReporting objects.

updateProgress

protected void updateProgress()
Calculate the average progress across all children. Uses integer arithmetic to insure that 100% progress must be reached when (and only when) all children are at 100%.

If there are no children, then progress is always 0%.
